#: OuchBrowser/Data/page.codeberg.shrimple.OuchBrowser.metainfo.xml:46
msgid ""
"Ouch Browser is a browser that utilizes the vertical tabs layout, which "
"allows for better tab management for more heavy browser users. Made for "
"focusing on your browsing, Ouch Browser comes with !bangs support, a multi-"
"purpose command palette, and mobile support."
msgstr ""

#: OuchBrowser/Data/page.codeberg.shrimple.OuchBrowser.metainfo.xml:53
msgid ""
